#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn47.45"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.45:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.45:0.2"
msgid "5. Amatavagga "
msgstr "5. The Deathless "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.45:0.3"
msgid "45. Kusalarāsisutta "
msgstr "45. A Heap of the Skillful "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn47.45:1.1"
msgid "“‘Kusalarāsī’ti, bhikkhave, vadamāno cattāro satipaṭṭhāne sammā vadamāno vadeyya. "
msgstr "“Rightly speaking, mendicants, you’d call these four kinds of mindfulness meditation a ‘heap of the skillful’. "

msgctxt "sn47.45:1.2"
msgid "Kevalo hāyaṃ, bhikkhave, kusalarāsi, yadidaṃ—cattāro satipaṭṭhānā. "
msgstr "For these four kinds of mindfulness meditation are entirely a heap of the skillful. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.187, sc2
msgctxt "sn47.45:2.1"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "sn47.45:2.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kāye kāyānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ; "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant meditates by observing an aspect of the body—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "

msgctxt "sn47.45:2.3"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe … "
msgstr "They meditate observing an aspect of feelings … "

msgctxt "sn47.45:2.4"
msgid "citte … pe … "
msgstr "mind … "

msgctxt "sn47.45:2.5"
msgid "dhammesu dhammānupassī viharati ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ. "
msgstr "principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.45:2.6"
msgid "‘Kusalarāsī’ti, bhikkhave, vadamāno ime cattāro satipaṭṭhāne sammā vadamāno vadeyya. "
msgstr "Rightly speaking, you’d call these four kinds of mindfulness meditation a ‘heap of the skillful’. "

msgctxt "sn47.45:2.7"
msgid "Kevalo hāyaṃ, bhikkhave, kusalarāsi, yadidaṃ—cattāro satipaṭṭhānā”ti. "
msgstr "For these four kinds of mindfulness meditation are entirely a heap of the skillful.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.45:2.8"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

